org.cef.network

Class CefResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefResponse

  • public abstract class CefResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent a web response. The methods of this class may be called on any thread.(用于表示web响应的类。这个类的方法可以在任何线程上调用。)
